PrecisAmendment, effective May 19, 1997, of Order in Council P.C. 1992-972 of May 13, 1992 as amended by Order in Council P.C. 1996-300 of March 12, 1996 which will extend the appointment of LAURENT MERCIER as part-time member of the National Farm Products Marketing Council until August 22, 1997.
